TripZip.TripDescription: Welcome to the Happiest Place on Earth! The ultimate family destination full of heart pounding rides and life long experiences. Come join Mickey Mouse and the gang and make memories that'll last a life time!

Scale the height of the historic Eiffel Tower and experience the breath taking views of Paris from the tower's observation deck. After experience the cultural melting pot that is Paris by browsing the shopping districts or partake in the culinary cuisine.

The Roman Colosseum is the ancient stadium where warriors known as gladiators fought to the death for the entertainment of the people. Tour these hallowed grounds and learn what I was like to be a gladiator.
Visit one of the seven wonders of the world! Witness one of the greatest archaeological structures of this era. Tour the ancient grounds and uncover the secrets of ancient Egypt.
Visit one of the seven wonders of the world! Witness what is called the ringing rocks and partake a structure that is mentioned within the tales of Arthurian Legend.
